token_stats/total_supply
***
The GraphQl query for this endpoint is:
``` graphql
query getTotalSupply($token: String!) {
  token_stats: laplace_token_stats_by_pk(token_name: $token) {
    block_height
    decimals
    token_name
    total_supply
  }
}

```
